///Surf_SlipperySlopes\\\
A ski / snowboarding, style surfmap based around a snow hotel/resort
High speed medium skill level surf map
This map is good for pretty much any gamemode

///Whats Uneque\\\
This map first of all surf down a hill
This map has invisable water
This map has all smooth ramps without rips
This map has a jail in the middle of spawn
This map has nice lighting
This map is full of secrets



This map is great for learning basic surfing skills, such as puddlehopping, telehopping, launching through hoops, and basic turning skills.

Every single bug in this map has been removed.
